Package com.back.isobus

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CanBUS_socket
    Class for opening and closing CAN bus interfaces and sending and receiving frames over the bus.
    Decoder
    This class receives an ISOBUS frame and decodes it into its fundamental parameters such as PGN, source address, priority, payloadInt, payload, header and msg it also prints it.
    FrameCAN
    This class defines a datatype for a CAN frame with timestamp.
    JSONObjectIterator
    Class for handling JSONObjects and JSONArrays
    Parser
    The Parser class is the main class used to parse messages from J1939-71 to a readable high level information.
    PGN
    This class collects all of the information related to the PGN field.
    SPN
    This class contains all the information of an SPN and converts the data received to the real value.
    SPN_data
    This class defines a datatype for a SPN group formed by opcodes.
